<topic id="topic_l3z_qq5_jm" xml:lang="en-US">
  <title>@dir attribute</title>
  <body>
    <dl>
      <dlentry>
        <dt>dir="ltr": </dt>
        <dd><p dir="ltr">Extensible Markup Language XML is a markup language that defines a set of rules for encoding documents in a format that is both human-readable and machine-readable.</p></dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry>
        <dt>dir="rtl": </dt>
        <dd><p dir="rtl">Extensible Markup Language XML is a markup language that defines a set of rules for encoding documents in a format that is both human-readable and machine-readable.</p></dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry>
        <dt>dir="rlo": </dt>
        <dd><p dir="rlo">Extensible Markup Language XML is a markup language that defines a set of rules for encoding documents in a format that is both human-readable and machine-readable.</p></dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>
    <p>The dir attribute is explained as follows:</p>
    <table>
      <title>dir attribute in DITA</title>
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry>Value</entry>
            <entry>Relevant CSS notation</entry>
          </row>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry>ltr</entry>
            <entry>direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>rtl</entry>
            <entry>direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>lro</entry>
            <entry>direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: bidi-override;</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>rlo</entry>
            <entry>direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: bidi-override;</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </table>
    <p>The dir attribute in HTML is explained as follows:</p>
    <table>
      <title>dir attribute and HTML element</title>
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry>Selector pattern</entry>
            <entry>Relevant CSS notation</entry>
          </row>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry>*[dir="ltr"]</entry>
            <entry>direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>*[dir="rtl"]</entry>
            <entry>direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>bdo[dir="ltr"]</entry>
            <entry>direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: bidi-override;</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>bdo[dir="rtl"]</entry>
            <entry>direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: bidi-override;</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </table>
